com.atakmap.android.routes.nav

Class NavigationUxManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.routes.nav.NavigationUxManager

  • public final class NavigationUxManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages the User Experience for navigation. It is responsible for ensuring the UI is shown and cleaned up at the appropriate times, that the cues are spoken as they should be, and any other User Experience related tasks are handled.
